        <a
          href="https://www.patreon.com/join/slowstitchclub"
          class="svelte-15xaass"
          >support me on Patreon</a
        >
        or follow on
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/slowstitchclub/"
          class="svelte-15xaass"
